# 用ack替换grep

[Ack](http://betterthangrep.com/)是一个给程序员用的grep, 使用perl regular expressions,
而不是POSIX/GNU subset.



#with grep

$ grep pattern $(find . -type f | grep -v '\\.svn') or $ grep -R --exclude-dir
.svn pattern



# with ack

$ ack pattern



# 只搜索ruby code

$ ack --ruby pattern



# mac

$ brew install ack



# ubuntu

$ sudo apt-get install ack-grep

